plugin.author: Socalabs
plugin.description:
Emulates MOS Technology SID of the Commodore 64
3 Oscillators
4 wave shapes: Square, Triangle, Saw, Noise
ADSR per oscillator
Ring modulation (replaces triangle output) and hard sync between oscillators
HP, BP, LP filters
Free / Open Source
Windows VST 32/64
Mac VST/AU 32/64
plugin.name: SID
